  <steps>
    <step num="0">Heat oil in a large pot over high heat. Cook onion until translucent. </step>
    <step num="1">Add beef, salt, and pepper, cooking until all the moisture has evaporated and the beef is browned. </step>
    <step num="2">Add crushed tomatoes, vodka, and chili flakes, stirring and cooking until half of the liquid has evaporated and the sauce has reduced. </step>
    <step num="3">Add cream, stirring until evenly incorporated. </step>
    <step num="4">Stir in pasta until evenly coated. </step>
    <step num="5">Serve with parsley and parmesan. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
